{"tid":2436400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲居台權 貿發局高層跳船","createTime":"2021-03-07T06:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T23:19:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"db50796e9f3d5540bdeb8b0a1c9e489ff56028bd","tid":2436400,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/KM5LVW7YJ5BFNBVSZN5RR2OHNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FKM5LVW7YJ5BFNBVSZN5RR2OHNA%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=1a3db8ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FKM5LVW7YJ5BFNBVSZN5RR2OHNA%2F&h=32b9b355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/KM5LVW7YJ5BFNBVSZN5RR2OHNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n獲居台權 貿發局高層跳船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LTn-Wvo-mj0cM9vWT3k8lFDGYmc=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XGUZ73JIWBBFDGVBWH6AXZER6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLTn-Wvo-mj0cM9vWT3k8lFDGYmc%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXGUZ73JIWBBFDGVBWH6AXZER6A.jpg&h=84173725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府跳船潮延伸至法定機構，貿易發展局台灣總經理潘慧心（圖）在香港駐台機構新春酒會上宣佈，她因個人生涯規劃將於本月底離開貿發局。消息稱潘在台任期屆滿後無意續聘，並已取得台灣居留權，據悉這種情況並不多見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陸委會無否認<br />\n<br />\n據台灣《聯合報》報道，香港經濟貿易文化辦事處、貿發局與旅發局3日晚在台北舉行新春酒會，潘慧心在致辭時透露離職訊息。對卸任後生涯規劃，潘不願多談，僅表示會留台。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n畢業於香港浸會大學傳理學系的潘慧心，1999年加入貿發局，曾先後派駐北京和洛杉磯，2017年轉調至台灣擔任總經理。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《聯合報》"},{"pid":"5f9fb702e642ec745bbef9a700c82233639d9ed5","tid":2436400,"uid":113000,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"正常啦<br />\n<br />\n係自由地區生活<br />\n<br />\n落地生根<br />\n<br />\n仲走番去極權獨裁地區做乜鳩"},{"pid":"86d1618428830a89a5ea6bc371bec9000ecc1194","tid":2436400,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"賣港賊"},{"pid":"1dfee257eef07d7461ee9e31c622b82110bf582d","tid":2436400,"uid":156511,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"好似北韓d外交官<br />\n有機會逃走"},{"pid":"e3c801661f0e79368039a29ad53508a26141dac3","tid":2436400,"uid":60145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"遲D比中共暗殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcb14736786cc6145c82cbbe62021e47ee559e6","tid":2436400,"uid":306614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f9fb702e642ec745bbef9a700c82233639d9ed5","tid":2436400,"uid":113000,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"正常啦<br />\n<br />\n係自由地區生活<br />\n<br />\n落地生根<br />\n<br />\n仲走番去極權獨裁地區做乜鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"啱呀 佢仲要咁有錢 直接退休都得啦"},{"pid":"24720befb7dbe1b9e2bbe220ad5c247bbdac7692","tid":2436400,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3c801661f0e79368039a29ad53508a26141dac3","tid":2436400,"uid":60145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"遲D比中共暗殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"肖健華 桂民海咁綁架送中"},{"pid":"4e9aec85c3f3e2c9dd6791bf58fdc084ae5a13f9","tid":2436400,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"脫港者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7ebaa8839989d0ecea9cbe52ba64f17af76364","tid":2436400,"uid":30868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"香港駐外外交人員投奔自由"},{"pid":"73c0f54b1949c5385489e1fd20620e13d634e728","tid":2436400,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"